{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 186292,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「希望が私の仕事だもの」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hope is my job.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186293,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふむ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186294,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　大したものだな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That's quite impressive.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186295,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「歴代法王は男ばかりだったが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"All the past pontiffs were men,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186296,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　神に抗おうとしたのは私の知る限り君達くらいだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"but as far as I know, you are among the few who tried to defy God.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186297,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「男と女の差……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The difference between men and women...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186298,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いや、そんなこともないか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, perhaps that isn't it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186299,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　君達が特別、変わり者なのだろう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You are probably just unusually eccentric.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186300,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私はもう何もする気が起きない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I no longer feel like doing anything.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186301,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だから手伝いはせんが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"So I won't help you,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186302,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　君達は頑張るといい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"but you should do your best.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186303,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「君は……アム・イスエルか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You are... Am Isuer, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186304,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あら、ご存じなのかしら？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh? You know of me?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186305,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ、少しだけだが。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, just a little.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186306,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　名前と……目指すものを、ね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Your name... and what you aim for.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186307,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「君のやり方は中々に面白い」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Your method is quite interesting.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186308,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だが無意味だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But it's meaningless.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186309,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「天文学的な時間をかけて",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It won't be impossible if you spend astronomical amounts of time,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186310,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　達成できないわけではない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"to achieve it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186311,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だが、それを成し遂げた後に、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But after you accomplish that,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186312,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　君は新たな絶望を知るだろう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"you will know a new despair.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186313,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（そう、別の神……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Yes, a different god...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186314,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いや、悪魔が支配する世界に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, the world will just be ruled by a demon instead,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186315,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　変わるだけだからね……）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"nothing but a change like that...)\")"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186316,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あら、平気よ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh, I'm fine.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186317,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「絶望には慣れてるもの」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I'm used to despair.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186318,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「むしろ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Rather...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186319,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今のやり方自体は間違いでないと聞けて、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I was even relieved to hear that the current approach itself isn't wrong,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186320,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　安心したくらいだわ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"that's how much reassured I was.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186321,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……君は根っからの聖職者のようだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...You seem to be a true cleric at heart.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186322,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だが、君の方は……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But you...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186323,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それほど献身的というわけでもないようだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"don't seem to be that devoted.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186324,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい、私はそれより即物的です」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, I am more pragmatic than that.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186325,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「聞きたいことがあり、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I have something I want to ask,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186326,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ここに来ました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"so I came here.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186327,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ルドラサウムの支配から",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Is there a way for humanity to escape\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186328,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　人類が逃れる方法はありますか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"from the rule of Rudrasaum?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186329,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さてね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186330,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さっきも言ったが……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"As I said earlier...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186331,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　この世界はルドラサウムのおもちゃ箱だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"this world is Rudrasaum's toy box.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186332,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おもちゃに飽きたら",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If it gets tired of its toys,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186333,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　我々は逃れられるかも知れないね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"maybe we could escape...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186334,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That is...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186335,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あまり考えたくないですね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"something I don't really want to think about.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186336,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だろうね。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I suppose so.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186337,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　飽きたおもちゃの行き場所は決まってる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The fate of toys that have been discarded is already decided.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186338,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「要はおもちゃの使い方が",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The problem is the way the toy is used\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186339,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あまりに悪趣味という話なんだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"is terribly in poor taste.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186340,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そういう子供に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"For a child like that,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186341,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それをやめさせる手と言えば……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"the way to stop that behavior is...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186342,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ママルドラサウムに説教でもしてもらうか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Maybe have Mama Rudrasaum lecture them.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186343,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ルドラサウムには母親がいるのですか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Does Rudrasaum have a mother?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186344,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186345,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ただの冗談だよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That was just a joke.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186346,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186347,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふっ、くく……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Heh, chuckle...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186348,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「方法なんてないと言っているのさ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I'm telling you, there is no method.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186349,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふむ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186350,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私はそろそろ寝させてもらう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I think I'll go to sleep soon.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186351,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　老体に夜更かしはこたえる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Staying up late is tough on this old body.\""
    }
  ]
}

